{"tid":1515665,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岑子杰佐敦遇持球棒鐵通男子　同行友人上前阻止遇襲","createTime":"2019-08-29T09:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T09:03:15.000Z","uid":268429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55fb46e97608df02a53b9d2484a415af95f91019","tid":1515665,"uid":268429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰的友人在佐敦遇襲受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發在中午近一時，岑子杰接受電話查詢時表示，當時與朋友在佐敦德興街一間餐廳內午飯之後，有兩名男子手持鐵通及球棒，當時對方怒目而視，之後就敲打枱面三下，兩人欲上前時，岑子杰同行友人上前阻止，遭該兩名男子襲擊，左手被打三棍受傷，左手出現紅腫瘀痕，已送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n早上在佐敦，岑子杰曾被一班表示要聲討民陣的人士包圍，雙方發生口角，指罵他是暴徒，又企圖搶他的揚聲器，警員其後介入仍有在場人士推撞，中午後他們散去。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477526-20190829.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477526-20190829.htm&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=7eb212c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477526-20190829.htm&h=1d21968d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477526-20190829.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8d86bc9f4ad869f22298d308bd62aded0db40b0d","tid":1515665,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}